### [ADMIN] 토큰 리프레쉬
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/refresh
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "refreshToken": "{{adminRefreshToken}}"
}

### [USER] 토큰 리프레쉬
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/refresh
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "refreshToken": "{{userRefreshToken}}"
}

